## Schema

### Required

- `name` (String) Name of the storage container
- `region_name` (String) Region name
- `tags` (String to String Map) Tags to apply to the storage container. Set to an empty map to remove all tags.

### Optional

- `service_name` (String) Service name. If omitted, the `OVH_CLOUD_PROJECT_SERVICE` environment variable is used.

### Read-Only

- `id` (String) Unique identifier for the resource (service_name/region_name/name)

